025/01/s25-square.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\n\n        \n        \n                            \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/tag/samsung-galaxy-s25/\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy S25\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\tSamsung Galaxy S25\n\t\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                                    \u003cp\u003eSamsung\u0026#39;s Galaxy S25 keeps things small without sacrificing power. With a Snapdragon 8 Elite processor, 12GB of RAM, and all sorts of tools courtesy of Galaxy AI, this is everything you expect from a modern flagship squeezed into a relatively svelte chassis.\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n                    \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n                    \n                        \u003cli\u003e        \n    \n                                \n        \n                            \n                                                            \n            \n                                                        \n            \n                                                        \n            \n            \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"b085-4999-99cb13fba572\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                            \n                        \t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-ur